水手服與機關槍-卒業 / Sailor Suit and Machine Gun –Graduation


上映日期 / 時間 / 院線:
Release Date:
01/07/2016


發行/主辦團體:
Organization:
驕陽電影 Sundream Motion Pictures


簡介:
Synopsis: 
曾經是黑幫老大的高中女生星泉 (橋本環奈 飾)，在成功復仇後與一眾手下金盤洗手，轉為在商店街經營咖啡店，在畢業前重新感受正常女高中生的愉快日常。可是因同學們誤中了模特兒騙案，代為出頭的星泉再次被捲入黑道鬥爭中，更發現自己的咖啡店竟然暗地裡牽涉毒品生意！為了查明真相、保護自己的地頭，星泉決定重出江湖，執起機關槍向敵人瘋狂掃射。

18-year-old high school girl Izumi once inherited leadership of a four-man yakuza gang, the Medaka Group. The group disbanded after a failed raid on the rival Hamaguchi gang. With graduation coming up, Izumi resumed her life as a high school student.
When her friends are caught in a scam by a fake modeling agency, and a dangerous new drug called ‘Cookie’ turns up at her school, Izumi investigates. When she questions the Hamaguchi boss, he in turn suspects the Medaka of drug dealing. Are the authorities trying to clean up the town by provoking a turf war?


導演： 
Director:
前田弘二  Koji Maeda


主演： 
Cast:
橋本環奈  Kana Hashimoto,, 
安藤政信  Hiroki Hasegawa
武田鐵矢  Tetsuya Takeda






 
 
 
 
 
 
 


© 2013 rthk.hk


















